com.calendarfx.view

Class DraggedEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.calendarfx.model.Entry<Object>
      • com.calendarfx.view.DraggedEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Entry<?>>

    public final class DraggedEntry
extends Entry<Object>
    Dragged entry is used internally only to represent the calendar entry that is currently being dragged. The entry wraps the original entry and stores some additional information about the ongoing drag.
